# Cloudflare Pages redirects / proxies for epilabs.org
#
# Do NOT add clean-URL → .html rewrites like:
#   /account /account.html 200
# Cloudflare Pages already serves account.html at /account (pretty URLs).
# Those rewrites cause infinite 308 redirect loops.
#
# Do NOT use SPA fallback (/* /index.html) for this multi-page static site —
# it masks missing pages by silently serving the homepage.

# ── API / backend proxy → Render ──
/api/* https://epi-verify-portal.onrender.com/api/:splat 200
/scitt/* https://epi-verify-portal.onrender.com/scitt/:splat 200
/.well-known/* https://epi-verify-portal.onrender.com/.well-known/:splat 200
